nekoga da mi popravi termostat.

320
00:34:31,857 --> 00:34:34,661
Soba mi gori. - Naravno gospodine,
poslaćemo servisera odmah.

321
00:34:35,362 --> 00:34:37,364
Hoćete?
- Naravno.

322
00:34:38,065 --> 00:34:39,767
