Upomoć!

373
00:44:33,730 --> 00:44:37,735
Vi! Gospodine!
Upomoć!

374
00:44:38,837 --> 00:44:40,838
Da! Da, vi!
Upomoć!

375
00:44:45,245 --> 00:44:47,448
Upomoć!
Vidite li me?!

376
